title: New ranked team looking for recruitment.
body:
People whom can enjoy playing together with us, communicate throughout the game, positive person. Preferably plays a lot.

It currently has 3 games left until ranked. {{summoner:30}}

replies.body: I'm keen if there's any room left. I'm online most days. :)
If there is any room left I wouldn't mind playing with you
I'll be sure to send you an invite.{{summoner:30}}
If you are interested, don't hesitate to add me in LOL. My name is 'Danieeeel'.
